</title>
<subSubSection id="CF1378130436F5356BE12403E23E0009" pageId="null" pageNumber="211" type="description">
<paragraph id="4C7F7639B6DD71C75D0EAB971F54F1D2" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="367E292EC861042A7AC674A5C9B29BB2" class="Aves" family="Fringillidae" genus="Linaria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Passeriformes" pageId="null" pageNumber="211" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="alpina">
<emphasis id="3517B82BEB865BBE6E0B006F79559837" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">
<authorityName id="0BE94C5E82200CC487518AA4EF681C2F" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">L.</authorityName>
alpina
</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 11) durch folgende Merkmale: Bis 20 cm hoch; 
<emphasis id="FFF20A50CCD625CD52D0609725291720" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Stengel vom Grund an bogig aufsteigend;</emphasis>
Kelchzipfel in der untern 
<normalizedToken id="2F01A850823410CEEE627DBEFF377F4E" originalValue="Hälfte" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Haelfte</normalizedToken>
am breitesten oder fast bis zur Spitze 
<pageBreakToken id="885A8DF5E39AEDBB1CECB9B5695CA464" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">gleich</pageBreakToken>
breit; 
<emphasis id="D9200B2AFBA8A0F5CAA75A554849F415" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Zipfel der Kronoberlippe 2</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="4A79DF52AF3A23DD14C8EA8D3FB7F43E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">
3mal so lang wie breit; Sporn 
<normalizedToken id="C291FB82AF194260EE5ECD10C4EB5667" originalValue="dünn" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">duenn</normalizedToken>
zylindrisch
</emphasis>
(
<emphasis id="D4F024D325EAD44F2B622012569FF0AD" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">nicht abgeflacht!</emphasis>
)
<emphasis id="51BCDE43330EADCC124E2D98FCB61867" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">; Samen 2,5</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="0EE3CBC8E06EF63493BFD219634B531F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">3 mm im Durchmesser.</emphasis>
- 
<normalizedToken id="394B9267466A5131EEEEF97BFE0892A4" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="57781380FE7149FCD90B90A9A1C1395B" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">
<emphasis id="2A4AC3A8D9E8BCE434C41039EBD2F408" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="C3CBC7BD10718FA8067912FE9FB40EB6" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">12:</emphasis>
Material vom Chasseral (Favarger 1949).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="7F2B7504BDB6E54298FB416BDCC04A89" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">
<emphasis id="0055CB9094421E1AB5C8391FAF2E6283" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Standort.</emphasis>
Subalpin und alpin. Beweglicher Kalkgrobschutt in sonnigen Lagen. 
<emphasis id="04CF842F201B61DD6B23FE1308A85DA2" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Erysimo-Kentranthetum</emphasis>
Jenny-Lips 1930.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="9AC755A1D11A245E1985F1259E1384CE" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">
<emphasis id="467826E64A37133269323E15815D538B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Verbreitung. Jura-Pflanze:</emphasis>
Jura (
<normalizedToken id="B958FECD20421E055804311F8F750258" originalValue="nordostwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">nordostwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis zum 
<normalizedToken id="01B0A32447D3D7D5C6ADEACBF3C55A39" originalValue="Weißenstein" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Weissenstein</normalizedToken>
); Savoyen (Dent 
<normalizedToken id="848C0430EF4D4378CC01769D13BC58D8" originalValue="d’Oche" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">d'Oche</normalizedToken>
?, La Tournette, Arpennoz, Mont Granier). Nach 
<normalizedToken id="A72DC341674B3A359C0C5FC12E55CD23" originalValue="Valdès" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Valdes</normalizedToken>
(1970) 
<normalizedToken id="C8685D9808E5FF5300037CDCDCA47C7D" originalValue="wächst" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">waechst</normalizedToken>
die Art auch 
<normalizedToken id="0D9BC6EEBE823FD33353D29869D190C1" originalValue="außerhalb" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">ausserhalb</normalizedToken>
des Gebiets in der 
<normalizedToken id="921E894DF137B1C979671A9CAA0D07BC" originalValue="Côte" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">Cote</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="BB66D21621F3C306E6D8B306916A9CE0" originalValue="d’Or" pageId="null" pageNumber="211">d'Or</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
